name: RenaisCat
description:
Renaissance means the new birth. 

As time is passing by, Precious Art has becoming privileges to certain groups of people; both on Buyer’s and Seller’s sides. 

But with NFT, everyone is equal again. New artists and new collectors are equal in trading and accessing to Art. It can be called that NFT is the new era of Art - the second renaissance!

You can notice that even this girl who has a robot friend is having a good time zipping wine, but her hand is tied with her phone for trading NFT all the time.

She also has a cat which is a symbol of rebirth and resurrection; per their nine lives. Cat has been with humans since ancient times and will always be with us through this Second Renaissance.
